data.description: Attention 55+ Home Buyers! If you COMPARE this Like-New, Energy-Efficient Nathan Carlisle home with others in Del Webb, you'll discover MORE value on a maintenance-free, SPACIOUS .174-acre lot, and for LESS cost! You Won't Believe the Backyard Outdoor Living Area! It's like your own personal retreat! Front yard HOA Maintenance is included, & the Backyard Paradise Living Area, with Pergola, is Lawncare FREE! Then, when you want to Swim, Exercise, or participate in planned activities, walk just two minutes away to the Isabella Village Activity Center! Or take the grandkids to the Amazing Club Savannah Resident Center & Water Park! 2 BDRM Floorplan with a dedicated Study, Lots of ceiling details, moldings, and Plantation Shutters throughout lend the right touches of luxury. A tastefully designed secondary bath, a large Utility Room, a spacious family room & Roomy Master Suite are all included. Ask for an Upgrade Sheet.
